description:
Carve your way through the Skullgirls cast with your gun-arm, hidden sawblades, and vicious taunts.

-Are you not entertained?! Give everyone a real performance in the Bunny Burrow, Black Dahlia's lair.
-Oh ho ho ho~! Dazzle your opponents with 29 intimidating palettes.
-Delight in the vengeful chaos of Black Dahlia's all new story mode.
-Become a master assassin with the help of Black Dahlia's new Character Tutorials!
name: Skullgirls: Black Dahlia
